\c 14
\s UJesu usilisa efundisa endlini yomFarisi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ekungeneni kwakhe ngesabatha endlini yomunye wabakhulu kubaFarisi ukuthi adle isinkwa\x + 7.36.\x*, bona basebemqaphela\x + Mark. 3.2. Luka 6.7. 20.20. 17.20.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo khangela, kwakukhona umuntu othile phambi kwakhe owayelombizankulu.
\v 3 UJesu wasephendula\x + 14.5. Hlu. 18.14.\x* wakhuluma lezazumthetho labaFarisi\x + Mat. 22.35.\x*, wathi: Kuvunyelwe yini ukusilisa ngesabatha\x + 13.14. Mat. 12.10.\x*?
\v 4 Kodwa bathula. Wase\add m\add*bamba wamsilisa wa\add m\add*yekela ukuthi ahambe.
\v 5 Wasebaphendula esithi\x + 14.5. Hlu. 18.14.\x*: Nguwuphi kini ongathi elobabhemi kumbe inkabi yakhe ewele emgodini, futhi angahle ayikhuphe ngosuku lwesabatha\x + 13.15.\x*?
\v 6 Abasazange babuyisele impendulo kuye ngalezizinto\x + Mat. 22.46.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Wasekhuluma umfanekiso kubo abanxusiweyo\x + Hlu. 14.12.\x*, ebona ukuthi bakhetha njani\x + Seb. 3.5.\x* izihlalo zabahloniphekayo\x + 14.8. Mat. 23.6.\x*, wathi kubo:
\v 8 Nxa unxusiwe ngumuntu emtshadweni\x + Mat. 22.2.\x*, ungahlali esihlalweni sabahloniphekayo\x + 14.8. Mat. 23.6.\x*; hlezi kukhona omkhulu kulawe onxusiweyo nguye,
\v 9 futhi okunxusileyo wena laye eze athi kuwe: Mxekele lo; khona uzaqala ukuhlala endaweni esekucineni usulenhloni\x + 3.8.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa nxa unxusiwe, hamba uhlale endaweni esekucineni\x + Zaga 25.6,7.\x*; ukuze, nxa efika okunxusileyo, athi kuwe: Mngane, yenyukela ngaphezulu; khona kuzakuba ludumo kuwe phambi kwabo abahlezi ekudleni lawe\x + 14.12. Mat. 20.13. 22.12. 26.50.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba wonke oziphakamisayo uzathotshiswa, lozithobayo uzaphakanyiswa\x + Mat. 23.12.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Wasesithi lakulowo owayemnxusile: Nxa usenza ukudla kwemini loba ukudla kwantambama, unganxusi abangane bakho, loba abafowenu, loba izihlobo zakho, loba omakhelwane abanothileyo; hlezi labo babuye bakunxuse, futhi ukwenananiswa kwenziwe kuwe\x + Mat. 22.4.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa nxa usenza idili\x + 5.29.\x*, nxusa abayanga, izilima, iziqhuli, iziphofu;
\v 14 njalo uzabusiswa, ngoba abalalutho lokukwenanisa\x + 14.21. Neh. 8.10,12. Esta 9.22.\x*; ngoba uzakwenaniselwa\x + Mat. 6.4.\x* ekuvukeni kwabalungileyo\x + Joha. 11.24. 1 Kor. 15.23. 1 Thes. 4.16. Isam. 20.4,5.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wedili lomtshado
\p
\v 15 Kwathi omunye kwababehlezi laye ekudleni esezwile lezizinto wathi kuye: Ubusisiwe lowo ozakudla isinkwa embusweni kaNkulunkulu\x + Isam. 19.9. Isa. 25.6. Luka 22.16,30.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kodwa wathi kuye: Umuntu othile wenza ukudla kwantambama okukhulu, wanxusa abanengi\x + Mat. 22.2-14.\x*.
\v 17 Ngesikhathi sokudla kwantambama wasethuma inceku yakhe ukuthi ithi kwabanxusiweyo: Wozani, ngoba sekulungisiwe konke.
\v 18 Kodwa bonke baqala omunye lomunye ukuzixolisela\x + Mat. 22.3.\x*. Owokuqala wathi kuye: Ngithenge insimu, ngimele ukuhamba ngiyeyibona; ngiyakuncenga, akungixolisele\x + Mat. 22.5.\x*.
\v 19 Lomunye wathi: Sengithenge izipane ezinhlanu zenkabi, ngiya ukuzilinga; ngiyakuncenga, akungixolisele.
\v 20 Lomunye wathi: Sengithethe umfazi, ngakho ngingeze ngeza\x + 1 Kor. 16.5.\x*.
\v 21 Isibuyile leyonceku yayibikela lezizinto inkosi yayo. Wasethukuthela umninindlu wathi encekwini yakhe: Phuma ngokuphangisa uye emigwaqweni lendleleni zomuzi, ulethe abayanga lezilima leziqhuli leziphofu ubangenise lapha\x + 14.13.\x*.
\v 22 Inceku yasisithi: Nkosi, sekwenziwe njengokulaya kwakho, njalo indawo isesekhona.
\v 23 Yasisithi inkosi encekwini: Phuma uye ezindleleni lezintangweni u\add ba\add*cindezele \add ba\add*ngene, ukuze igcwaliswe indlu yami\x + Mat. 22.9.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba ngithi kini: Kakho kulamadoda ayenxusiwe ozakuzwa ukudla kwami kwantambama\x + Mat. 21.41,43.\x*.
\s Abafundi bakaJesu abaqotho
\p
\v 25 Kwakuhamba laye amaxuku amanengi; wasetshibilika wathi kuwo:
\v 26 Uba umuntu esiza kimi\x + Mat. 10.37. Dute. 13.6-8. 33.9.\x*, futhi engazondi uyise, lonina, lomkakhe, labantwana, labafowabo, labodadewabo\x + Mat. 6.24. Luka 16.13. Roma 9.13. Mal. 1.3.\x*, yebo ngitsho leyakhe impilo, angebe ngumfundi wami\x + Joha. 12.25. Seb. 20.24. Isam. 12.11.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo loba ngubani\x + Mat. 10.38.\x* ongathwali isiphambano sakhe angilandele, angebe ngumfundi wami\x + Joha. 19.17.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Ngoba nguwuphi kini, othi efuna ukwakha umphotshongo, ongaqali ahlale phansi, abale indleko, ukuthi ulakho yini okokuqedisa?
\v 29 Ukuze hlezi, kuthi esebekile isisekelo kodwa angabi lamandla okuqeda, bonke abakubonayo baqale ukumhleka,
\v 30 besithi: Lumuntu waqala ukwakha, kodwa kabanga lamandla okuqeda\x + Zaga 24.27.\x*.
\v 31 Loba yiyiphi inkosi ezakuya empini imelene lenye inkosi engaqali ihlale phansi inakane ngokuthi ilamandla yini ngenkulungwane ezilitshumi okuhlangabezana laleyo\x + Jobe 15.24.\x* eza ilenkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili ukumelana layo\x + Hlab. 68.17.\x*?
\v 32 Kodwa uba kunge\add njalo\add*, ingathi isekhatshana leyo, ithume amanxusa icele okokuthula.
\v 33 Ngakho kunjalo wonke kini ongadeli konke alakho, angeke aba ngumfundi wami\x + 9.61.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Itshwayi lihle\x + Mark. 9.50.\x*; kodwa uba itshwayi seliduma, lizavuselelwa ngani\x + Mat. 5.13.\x*\x + Mark. 9.50.\x*?
\v 35 Kalifanele lamhlabathi ledundulu lomquba\x + 9.62.\x*; kodwa liyalahlwa ngaphandle\x + Mat. 5.13.\x*. Olendlebe zokuzwa, akezwe\x + Mat. 11.15.\x*.